Release notes: Link

2. microsd에 os 저장
image 프로그램에서 os 선택, 저장소 선택 write 선택 

3. microsd에 꼿고 전원케이블 연결 

4. apt-get update
   apt-get install openvswitch-switch openvswitch-common bridge-utils
   ovs-vsctl add-br ovsbr0
   ovs-vsctl add-port ovsbr0 eth0
   ovs-vsctl add-port ovsbr0 eth1
   ovs-ofctl dump-ports ovsbr0
   ovs-ofctl dump-flows ovsbr0 
   ovs-vsctl set-controller ovsbr0 tcp:192.68.59.100:6633
   ovs-vsctl show
  
5. ovs interface와 route interface는 중복되지 않게

   
